  <brief_title>Effect of an Electronic Cognitive Aid Versus Static Cognitive Aid on the Management of a Simulated Crisis</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of an Electronic Dynamic Cognitive Aid Versus a Static Cognitive Aid on the Management of a Simulated Crisis</official_title>
